data.description:
Your second chance, their loss, your gain! $10,000 in concessions with acceptable offer!
This awesome home in Bushland ISD is back on the market, and here's your chance to make it yours. Revel in spacious living with four bedrooms, three bathrooms, and a detached man cave/workshop/extra garage awaiting your personal touch. The dream kitchen boasts a huge granite island for lively conversations. Entertain in style or unwind on the covered patio, savoring the outdoors. Act fast—turn their loss into your gain and schedule your showing today!
